    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80de-841f-ed81d8b25814",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper explores Learning Process-consistent KT (LPKT), a model that monitors the learning process. The model incorporates parameters to account for learning gains and forgetting. They add a new constraint to their model to account for student-specific learning rates. Results on 3 public datasets show hat PLKT and LPKT-S outperformed State-of-the-art models.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80de-841f-ed81d8b25814",
        "parent": {
